Leicester defender Ritchie De Laet has signed a new four-year contract with the club.

The 25-year-old Belgian has started all 11 of the Foxes' Barclays Premier League games this season.

De Laet told the club's official website: 'I'm so happy to sign a new deal here at Leicester.

